readable.content: A girl jumps over the grass tufts on a sandy area near the sea . A girl running through uneven sand with some withered grass . A girl wearing a jacket and scarf is playing on the beach . A little girl is jumping down a sandy hill . A small girl wearing a green shirt jumping off a grassy , sandy hill with a black scarf in her hand .
